basic_info.long_description: Altisource Asset Management Corporation engages in the provision of asset management and corporate governance services for institutional investors in the United States. The company offers its services under a residential asset management agreement to Altisource Residential Corporation, which acquires and owns single-family rental assets. It also provides management services to NewSource Reinsurance Company Ltd. The company was founded in 2012 and is headquartered in Frederiksted, Virgin Islands.
